headline: Jacobs - Mott MacDonald Consortium Appointed as Design Development Partner for Transformative UK Transit Program
summary: A Jacobs (NYSE: J) and Mott MacDonald consortium has been appointed as the Design Development Partner by the West Yorkshire Combined Authority (The CA) in the next phase of the West Yorkshire Mass Transit Programme – an advanced, high-capacity public transport system to be integrated with cycling, walking and rail, to connect communities across the region.
